data.description: Welcome to your new home nestled within the Golden Meadows neighborhood in South Bossier. Offering 3 Bedrooms and 2 baths to assure no wait.  The beautiful back yard has a covered patio for entertaining guest. There is also a fairly new shed in the back for storage. Windows were replaced in the last five years. The hot water heater is less than a year old. The master bathroom offers a walk-in tub. Come see this wonderful community in South Bossier with award winning schools and minutes from restaurants & shopping.
